{"tid":2165509,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱黎智英「勇者」 特朗普：給他最好的祝福","createTime":"2020-08-20T01:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T01:13:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d1d634548c3f7e03bc417bcf2d3ffd5df8be08","tid":2165509,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普周三稱壹傳媒創辦人黎智英為「勇者」，並向他表達支持。今次特朗普一周內第二度評論黎智英被捕事件。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮向記者表示，黎智英是「了不起的君子」，「當然是勇者」，並給予黎智英最好的祝福。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方上周一以涉嫌觸犯港版國安法為由拘捕黎智英，並大規模搜查蘋果日報大樓。他上周三凌晨獲准保釋。特朗普上周四曾形容黎智英被捕為「可怕事情」。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200820/6FLKGFXKYFFKTPFMRTQCNWOK7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200820%2F6FLKGFXKYFFKTPFMRTQCNWOK7Y%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufZ4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=98702584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200820%2F6FLKGFXKYFFKTPFMRTQCNWOK7Y%2F&h=8343bd37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200820/6FLKGFXKYFFKTPFMRTQCNWOK7Y/</a>"}]}